description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Whole Body Circuit ' from the channel Rina Thomas.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights and Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Adrenaline Rush and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The The Adrenaline Rush vibe means Heart-racing, full-body intensity, unpredictable challenges. This is especially good for Those who crave challenge, variety, and adrenaline. The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Total body work with dumbbells off Hydrow and recovery efforts on Hydrow. 

Max rhythm: 24, Format: AMRAP...
